{
  "stem": "13833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Schutzpass means exactly 'protective pass.' And on the protective pass, in two languages-- in German and in Hungarian-- it said that the 'above holder of this paper and all his belongings are protected by the Swedish government.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when and if we can collectively leave for Sweden, then in Sweden, this paper will be invalid in 14 days.' That's what it says.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The signature on it is our ambassador.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, they called him Minister Danielsson, not Raoul Wallenberg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, first of all, he gave it to all his helpers' parents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, like, my parents got it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I went back to my parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, out!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Papi said, but, but we have that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, just come home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Let's, let's see what's happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't want you in this Jewish house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Here, you have the paper of Raoul's.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Thanks God, nothing happened then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But then my cousin came, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The mother didn't want her to leave the house yet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But my cousin, she also came home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Raoul went to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I don't know how much he paid them or what.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But he was-- he spoke perfect German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the Germans didn't have an embassy anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So the foreign-- the neutral countries took care of their stuff.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when Raoul wanted something-- he was 7 foot tall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he said in German to them, if you don't do what I'm telling you, then we will not take care of your stuff.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they get mail, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to take care of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wouldn't give it to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You don't do what I want, you don't get anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, he--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
